high_descs: turn around and walk to the kitchen counter on your right next to the sink
pick up a knife from the counter to the left of the sink
move to the right a bit and face the sink
slice the apple on the left side inside the sink
place the knife inside of the sink
grab an apple slice out of the kitchen sink
turn around and walk over to the microwave on the left corner of the room
place the apple inside of the microwave, let it cook, then take it back out
turn around and walk to the opposite side of the room, then hang a right and walk to the black table on the left side of the kitchen counter
place the apple on top of the black table
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple slice on top of the black table

high_descs: turn to face the white counter
pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the left side of the counter
move to the right to face the sink
cut a piece off of the apple
put the knife in the sink next to the apple
pick up the small piece of the apple
turn right to go across the room to the microwave in the right corner of the room
open the microwave door, put the apple on the plate in the microwave, close the door, set the timer for 5 seconds and start, open the door and pick up the apple from the plate
turn around and go across to the other side of the room with the apple
put the apple in front of the coffee mug that is sitting on the black table that is to the left of the counter
anns.task_desc: put a slice of cooked apple on the black table

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick up the knife off of the counter.
Move to the right to face the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into 3 parts.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up one slice of the apple.
Turn around and go to the left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, wait a few seconds then remove the apple.
Go to the left in front of the black shelf.
Place the apple on the black shelf.
